## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="57460-275">下列範例會使用合成器能夠暢所欲言預設音訊輸出的片語。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="57460-275">The following example uses the synthesizer to speak a phrase to the default audio output.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;  
using System.Speech.Synthesis;  
  
namespace SampleSynthesis  
