## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="57460-321">下列範例會建立<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.Prompt>從字串的物件，並將物件傳遞的引數為<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="57460-321">The following example creates a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.Prompt> object from a string and passes the object as an argument to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
